{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 4",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-535239472732701924 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/smooth-spine/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=535239472514598116&sectionId=535239472732701924)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUdLMEjEBz_text","label":"ggUdLMEjEBz_text","default":"Leading Physical Therapy Specialist: <strong>This Is The Best Way to Sleep Pain-Free Through The Night</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg4xxxACX_V_text","label":"gg4xxxACX_V_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:#FFBF00;\">If you suffer from Sciatica pain in your lower back, hips, or legs,</span> <span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,255,255,0);\">leading to sleepless nights and waking up stiff and sore, </span>read this short article right now before you do anything else.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_FPFkw98r_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg_FPFkw98r_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-5bf8297a-9c56-4d2d-bc80-2f1c2ef7f9c7.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggE15XdiBTy_text","label":"ggE15XdiBTy_text","default":"4,684 Ratings"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHhh9o2n5H_youtubeUrl","label":"ggHhh9o2n5H_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHhh9o2n5H_vimeoUrl","label":"ggHhh9o2n5H_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggHhh9o2n5H_html5Url","label":"ggHhh9o2n5H_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/44f8b6872c5d4fba98ac18a6118c861a.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7BmL-pOf5_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg7BmL-pOf5_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-7c8734ef-2aa6-49ff-a685-3b012371254a.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggV3rzNuWDx_text","label":"ggV3rzNuWDx_text","default":"By W. Patton <i>(Medical Reporter)</i>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsGGsqiuqp_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggsGGsqiuqp_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-261c4155-0f60-4f68-8a7d-c043d07e9344.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gggkRgFYHFR_text","label":"gggkRgFYHFR_text","default":"<p>I’ve been a reporter in the medical industry for 10 years now, and experts finally have found a solution…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_gUCj4Y73_text","label":"gg_gUCj4Y73_text","default":"<p>A renowned physical therapist with years of experience treating patients for sciatica, lower back and hip pain, says that <strong>proper sleep support is crucial to overall spinal health.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBxFcQqeeP_text","label":"ggBxFcQqeeP_text","default":"<p>Most of his patients suffer from issues that stem from years of <strong>poor sleeping positions</strong> and insufficient support.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCEXcsnt2K_text","label":"ggCEXcsnt2K_text","default":"<p>Let’s face it—waking up in pain is no way to start your day.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiQTNI8qdP_text","label":"ggiQTNI8qdP_text","default":"<p>If you’re like most people, you probably <strong>wake up with a stiff back, sore hips, or even shooting pain down your legs.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7T9_xAWJ1_text","label":"gg7T9_xAWJ1_text","default":"<p>And while you may think it’s just part of getting older, the truth is, the way you sleep could be the real problem.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggI9wifD87C_text","label":"ggI9wifD87C_text","default":"<p>How Sleeping the Wrong Way Can Damage Your Back and Hips</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9t23R6ZNB_youtubeUrl","label":"gg9t23R6ZNB_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9t23R6ZNB_vimeoUrl","label":"gg9t23R6ZNB_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"gg9t23R6ZNB_html5Url","label":"gg9t23R6ZNB_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/e1ae5ea6d685432d997c4a85215930b1.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCuPVsYfdL_text","label":"ggCuPVsYfdL_text","default":"<p>Did you know that how you sleep can mess up your back and hips?&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggI1umGb4p2_text","label":"ggI1umGb4p2_text","default":"<p><strong>If you’re a side sleeper</strong>, like many of us, you might be putting pressure on your spine without even knowing it.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYTmbm5iFw_text","label":"ggYTmbm5iFw_text","default":"<p>Sleeping without proper support causes your spine to fall out of alignment, which puts pressure on your spinal discs, and results in <strong>agonizing pain in your lower back and hips.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMItpKCkbc_text","label":"ggMItpKCkbc_text","default":"<p>Over time, this also leads to nerve problems like sciatica, where the big nerve that runs from your lower back to your legs gets pinched, <strong>causing sharp shooting pain or a constant dull ache.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglWI5DP5CZ_text","label":"gglWI5DP5CZ_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:33px;\"><strong>The Hidden Root Cause of Sciatica, Hip, and Lower Back Pain</strong></span></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA9IeRVVkU_youtubeUrl","label":"ggA9IeRVVkU_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA9IeRVVkU_vimeoUrl","label":"ggA9IeRVVkU_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA9IeRVVkU_html5Url","label":"ggA9IeRVVkU_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/5a04680dc4e14541a23d15bdc57d9291.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAAICOK6bL_text","label":"ggAAICOK6bL_text","default":"<p>Sciatica can be a real nightmare—if you’ve ever felt that burning pain starting in your lower back or hip and running down your leg, you know how bad it can get.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwxw8zLyld_text","label":"ggwxw8zLyld_text","default":"<p>This happens when your spine isn’t properly aligned, and the nerves get squeezed by the discs.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggte62TLDZ4_text","label":"ggte62TLDZ4_text","default":"<p><strong>All you need is a way to reduce this pressure by keeping your spine and hips in a neutral straight position, which stops the nerve from getting pinched.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQ_ZqK6AxA_text","label":"ggQ_ZqK6AxA_text","default":"<p>This would mean less pain, fewer flare-ups, and a much better chance of waking up feeling refreshed, instead of dreading the day ahead.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggl0QT2hUMI_text","label":"ggl0QT2hUMI_text","default":"<p>&nbsp;Cumulative Pressure on Intervertebral Discs</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggscEwAbIuB_youtubeUrl","label":"ggscEwAbIuB_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggscEwAbIuB_vimeoUrl","label":"ggscEwAbIuB_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggscEwAbIuB_html5Url","label":"ggscEwAbIuB_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/92bdcf0e6462400e89be2c7d2c1c02f2.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIDaynodIh_text","label":"ggIDaynodIh_text","default":"<p>Your spine is made up of bones that have little cushions (called discs) between them.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg82fWlvyF4_text","label":"gg82fWlvyF4_text","default":"<p>These discs help your spine move and absorb pressure. <strong>But when you sleep in a misalignment position</strong>, the weight of your body can push down too hard on these discs, causing pain or even leading to bigger problems like herniated discs.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQPCGIh3R1_text","label":"ggQPCGIh3R1_text","default":"<p><strong>You can prevent this from happening by maintaining proper spine alignment.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQHx3nB57F_text","label":"ggQHx3nB57F_text","default":"<p>With the right level of firmness and support, you could keep your spine in their correct positions, distributing pressure evenly across your back rather than concentrating it on specific areas.&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggdtfYcuLF_text","label":"gggdtfYcuLF_text","default":"<p><strong>This would significantly reduce the risk of disc problems</strong>, whether you’re already experiencing pain or looking to prevent it from happening.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaeUau61Sv_text","label":"ggaeUau61Sv_text","default":"<p>How the SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow will help you sleep AND wake up Pain-Free</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMNpygy9kE_text","label":"ggMNpygy9kE_text","default":"<p>That’s where the SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow comes in—this isn’t just a regular pillow; it’s a <strong>scientifically designed solution to help align your spine, reduce pain, and prevent further damage.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLczMDdfzG_text","label":"ggLczMDdfzG_text","default":"<p>Say Goodbye to Pinched Nerves, Hip Pain, and Back Discomfort</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gghT_gjY1FV_youtubeUrl","label":"gghT_gjY1FV_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"gghT_gjY1FV_vimeoUrl","label":"gghT_gjY1FV_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"gghT_gjY1FV_html5Url","label":"gghT_gjY1FV_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/0cb3f43ad0174bd19726b49d61088395.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi6Cz2z6R1_text","label":"ggi6Cz2z6R1_text","default":"<p>A major issue for most side sleepers is hip pain, which is often caused by bone-on-bone contact or poor support for the lower body.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcea02BdOV_text","label":"ggcea02BdOV_text","default":"<p><strong>Our Pillow helps relieve sciatica pain by reducing pressure on your lower back and hips, preventing nerve impingement as you sleep.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7PP_PdUoQ_text","label":"gg7PP_PdUoQ_text","default":"<p>This reduction in compression allows your muscles and discs to relax and recover naturally, giving you relief from that burning, stabbing pain you feel when you wake up.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaGiA6cJXj_text","label":"ggaGiA6cJXj_text","default":"<p>The <strong>SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow</strong> tackles this issue head-on by ensuring proper alignment of your spine and hips, creating a balanced position that prevents nerve pinching and alleviates pressure on sensitive areas.&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggvLvmR4MTC_text","label":"ggvLvmR4MTC_text","default":"<p>By cradling your hips and legs, the pillow helps maintain optimal alignment, ensuring that you don’t wake up with aching hips or a stiff lower back.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRrargy9cE_text","label":"ggRrargy9cE_text","default":"<p>Why the <a href=\"https://smoothspine.com/products/pres-alp\"><u>SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow</u></a> Stands Out</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDTVeHMtS2_youtubeUrl","label":"ggDTVeHMtS2_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDTVeHMtS2_vimeoUrl","label":"ggDTVeHMtS2_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDTVeHMtS2_html5Url","label":"ggDTVeHMtS2_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/15f4ee7366ea4ba6b438422ab0b270cf.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7lnWFIkKi_text","label":"gg7lnWFIkKi_text","default":"<p>There are plenty of pillows that claim to help with sleep and pain relief, but few deliver on those promises like the <i>SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow</i>. What sets it apart?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_0","label":"ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_0","default":"<p><strong>Optimal Spine Alignment:</strong> Ensures your spine remains aligned throughout the night, relieving pressure on intervertebral discs.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_1","label":"ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_1","default":"<p><strong>Targeted Pain Relief:</strong> Reduces lower back pain, hip discomfort, and sciatica by preventing nerve impingement.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_2","label":"ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_2","default":"<p><strong>Moves With You:</strong> Stays in place when turning over, so you don&#039;t wake up having to readjust it.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_3","label":"ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_3","default":"<p><strong>Perfect Firmness:</strong> Strikes the ideal balance between softness and support, cradling your body without collapsing under your weight.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_4","label":"ggS7Eu6ffCC_childItem_4","default":"<p><strong>Breathable, Cool Design:</strong> Stays cool throughout the night, preventing heat build-up that can disturb sleep.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwp-GYo-qD_text","label":"ggwp-GYo-qD_text","default":"<p>Invest in Your Health—Start Sleeping Pain-Free</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg96ubj9Zf6_youtubeUrl","label":"gg96ubj9Zf6_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"gg96ubj9Zf6_vimeoUrl","label":"gg96ubj9Zf6_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"gg96ubj9Zf6_html5Url","label":"gg96ubj9Zf6_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/f560d53c857b483d9f37b2e6ad9f9822.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"gga-vYQrFc9_text","label":"gga-vYQrFc9_text","default":"<p>The SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow isn’t just a pillow—<strong>it’s a long-term investment in your spinal health</strong>.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggV-NkPO7Iq_text","label":"ggV-NkPO7Iq_text","default":"<p>By correcting poor posture, relieving pressure on your discs, and reducing nerve impingement, this pillow helps you <strong>sleep better and live pain-free</strong>.&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggi6Iz0Lcb5_text","label":"ggi6Iz0Lcb5_text","default":"<p>Whether you’re suffering from sciatica, chronic back pain, or just want to prevent future issues, the SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow is the solution you need.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqkiLYl4sK_text","label":"ggqkiLYl4sK_text","default":"<p>Order today and start your journey toward pain-free, restful sleep.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg-sLpTOIrs_text","label":"gg-sLpTOIrs_text","default":"<p>How It Feels and What to Expect</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8p2-eUE0s_text","label":"gg8p2-eUE0s_text","default":"<p>After the first night of using SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow, you'll notice a big difference in how well you slept. The unqiue design ensures your spine is aligned and stable. As you finally align your spinal discs properly, you’ll experience a gentle, peaceful sensation that also <strong>helps you fall asleep pain-free</strong>.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_uoNW6MjH_text","label":"gg_uoNW6MjH_text","default":"<p>&nbsp;Night-by-Night Relief and Progress</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIEcUkNB1k_youtubeUrl","label":"ggIEcUkNB1k_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIEcUkNB1k_vimeoUrl","label":"ggIEcUkNB1k_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIEcUkNB1k_html5Url","label":"ggIEcUkNB1k_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/0260b19487254840b1feb6d101cc145d.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIYpqjeYTB_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggIYpqjeYTB_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-4f81447a-884d-40b9-ac8c-abef62b4e870.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3ic8VwSJq_text","label":"gg3ic8VwSJq_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong>Day 1:</strong></span> From the very first use, you may notice a reduction in discomfort and a better night's sleep without many interruptions.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggiYNKFHqnP_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggiYNKFHqnP_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-cd1daff8-554b-4b84-81dc-d94594b17761.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCGayFa8Wz_text","label":"ggCGayFa8Wz_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong>Day 7:</strong></span> By the end of the first week, the consistent nighttime support may contribute to reducing your discomfort completely. You might feel more mobile and possibly less dependent on pain relief methods.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggaxxL1Cc7D_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggaxxL1Cc7D_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-6d97532c-c0e5-488b-989d-045abbd965d2.png"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1fg54qodK_text","label":"gg1fg54qodK_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong>Day 14:</strong></span> At two weeks, you might find your posture improved as the pillow helps encourage your muscles to maintain proper alignment. Nights of sleep get longer with less waking up, and your ability to perform daily activities could increase.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLE1HiR_pg_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggLE1HiR_pg_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-d8f79620-26aa-44d0-b255-c9a614cd2079.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrDTyd2ZIf_text","label":"ggrDTyd2ZIf_text","default":"<p><span style=\"color:#FF0000;\"><strong>Day 30:</strong></span> After a month of using the Alignment Pillow, you may experience a noticeable improvement in your overall quality of life and energy levels. Your sciatica discomfort might be significantly reduced, if not alleviated, and you could feel more active, comfortable, and confident.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEw6PwgKBF_text","label":"ggEw6PwgKBF_text","default":"<p>Real People, Real Relief</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwFOU8yG2c_text","label":"ggwFOU8yG2c_text","default":"<p>At the moment of writing this, thousands of people around the world are using the SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow <strong>to relieve their sciatica, hip pain and lower back pain.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2GbzcbiVU_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg2GbzcbiVU_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-774247ee-6407-4926-8ca5-e77215af0472.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSiqFIbMxg_text","label":"ggSiqFIbMxg_text","default":"<p>AS SEEN ON&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBBhHs9iym_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggBBhHs9iym_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://ucarecdn.com/f0fd2cb0-0ec0-47b9-9ade-60feba9841e5/-/format/auto/-/preview/1500x1500/-/quality/lighter/3%20_2_.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggveNFtWcks_text","label":"ggveNFtWcks_text","default":"<p>This pillow has helped thousands of people to relieve their Sciatica, hip pain, and lower back discomfort. <u>The best part?</u> You ONLY need to slide it on before you go to sleep.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEQocTiPmV_text","label":"ggEQocTiPmV_text","default":"<p>No special exercise plan or strict schedule like with other health solutions, no need to change any of your routines either. And as a result you will reap the sleep and<strong> relief benefits for the WHOLE night</strong>.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_2GpDNkML_youtubeUrl","label":"gg_2GpDNkML_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_2GpDNkML_vimeoUrl","label":"gg_2GpDNkML_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_2GpDNkML_html5Url","label":"gg_2GpDNkML_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/f215f213eaa84ab6877b3424f06d4477.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGRaNAAs7-_text","label":"ggGRaNAAs7-_text","default":"<p>And I’m confident that it’s going to help you too.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDrmdSIbID_text","label":"ggDrmdSIbID_text","default":"<p>Just imagine how your life would look like:</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpXBCMw42T_childItem_0","label":"ggpXBCMw42T_childItem_0","default":"<p>No more struggling to get out of bed in the morning feeling stiff and sore.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpXBCMw42T_childItem_1","label":"ggpXBCMw42T_childItem_1","default":"<p>No more sleepless nights because of sharp nerve pain.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggpXBCMw42T_childItem_2","label":"ggpXBCMw42T_childItem_2","default":"<p>No more discomfort during the day that keeps you from enjoying life.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzyMze2ycm_text","label":"ggzyMze2ycm_text","default":"<p>Our team is working around the clock to create enough SmoothSpine™️ Pillows for everyone in need.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGkHY4dMUC_text","label":"ggGkHY4dMUC_text","default":"<p>But I hate to admit that we are currently failing at that - <strong>the demand is just too big</strong>.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLuejGCamZ_text","label":"ggLuejGCamZ_text","default":"<p>Folks who have tested the SmoothSpine™️ Alignment Pillow and experienced the relief are now asking us for more devices for their families and friends.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggMwomynm1s_text","label":"ggMwomynm1s_text","default":"<p><strong>All this makes our stock run out quickly every time we get a new shipment.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWB0CXWiHs_text","label":"ggWB0CXWiHs_text","default":"<p>Now, if you are reading this article, it means that we probably have a few pillows left in stock, otherwise, we would’ve taken the page down.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoFfORPDNH_text","label":"ggoFfORPDNH_text","default":"<p>But unfortunately, we cannot guarantee for how much longer…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAiumAnsu7_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggAiumAnsu7_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-b585c819-788e-4b54-b8c2-3ff8daa9b9ab.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQiDl3-5ob_text","label":"ggQiDl3-5ob_text","default":"<p>Once we run out of stock…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggj87A7_vEk_text","label":"ggj87A7_vEk_text","default":"<p>It could take us till the end of the year to get back in stock because these products take quite a long time to make.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSDELymd7F_text","label":"ggSDELymd7F_text","default":"<p><strong>So if you are serious about reducing pain and discomfort in your hips and lower back…</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA2ElEw_Qk_text","label":"ggA2ElEw_Qk_text","default":"<p>I recommend you DO NOT leave this page… Because this may be <strong>THE ONLY CHANCE</strong> to get the relief you were praying for.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggz8tUDHp1Q_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggz8tUDHp1Q_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0252/1261/6781/files/gempages_464015397612422087-ab6521f9-fdc0-492f-924b-57e126feb6be.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRPepLCka5_text","label":"ggRPepLCka5_text","default":"<p>To put it into perspective, when SmoothSpine hired business &amp; marketing consultants to help us launch the pillow to the market, they told them to charge $80.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZEa261484_text","label":"ggZEa261484_text","default":"<p>It certainly made sense from the business perspective.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmoxxDhoI-_text","label":"ggmoxxDhoI-_text","default":"<p><strong>But SmoothSpine founders are not greedy businessmen.</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCjfJvN5Wr_text","label":"ggCjfJvN5Wr_text","default":"<p>And the only goal with this pillow is to help as many people as possible.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggC713UQZ0J_text","label":"ggC713UQZ0J_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:#FFBF00;\">And that is why We Priced It At 1/2</span> of What All the Experts Recommended</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLDkfOPlsA_youtubeUrl","label":"ggLDkfOPlsA_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLDkfOPlsA_vimeoUrl","label":"ggLDkfOPlsA_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLDkfOPlsA_html5Url","label":"ggLDkfOPlsA_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/3dd82280636141758421ac1dd85754ab.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmQFPhG7Yu_text","label":"ggmQFPhG7Yu_text","default":"<p>So even if you use it for just one year...</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYjtVoUMjq_text","label":"ggYjtVoUMjq_text","default":"<p><strong>That's only a fraction of the cost of what you would spend for therapy - $100s of dollar just per one session!</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQnOM32ssM_text","label":"ggQnOM32ssM_text","default":"<p>And guess what? You'll probably use it way more than that.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggbgKrzh07M_text","label":"ggbgKrzh07M_text","default":"<p><strong>You’re Welcome to Test the Pillow for<u> 90 Nights</u>, 100% Risk-Free!</strong></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQpqedqKxP_youtubeUrl","label":"ggQpqedqKxP_youtubeUrl","default":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cyzh48XRS4M"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQpqedqKxP_vimeoUrl","label":"ggQpqedqKxP_vimeoUrl","default":"https://vimeo.com/347119375"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQpqedqKxP_html5Url","label":"ggQpqedqKxP_html5Url","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/5bfd4c576fc24e76a1936845cedb8c19.mp4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggswJ_2mMaX_text","label":"ggswJ_2mMaX_text","default":"<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">That’s right!</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>You have a generous 90-night TRIAL period.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>You have 90 nights to test the SmoothSpine Pillow and see if it works for you.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">If it lives up to its promise, you’re welcome to hold onto it for relief from Sciatica pain, hip pain and lower back discomfort.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">But if you’re not happy with your purchase for ANY reason…</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">And you think there are better solutions out there…</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">Simply let us know within the next 90 days, and </span><strong>you’ll receive a full refund</strong><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\"> on the same day, no questions asked.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">Whether it’s 89 minutes or 89 days after your purchase…</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">Our SmoothSpine Team is committed to ensuring you only pay if you’re 100% satisfied with the product. If not, it’s our responsibility.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Sounds good?</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">And don’t worry…</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">Our team is easily reachable for any assistance.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">You can email us at <strong>support@smoothspine.com</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">Our customer success team is always on standby and will respond to your queries </span><strong>WITHIN HOURS.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">Now that’s a real </span><strong>RISK-FREE deal</strong><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:rgb(47,47,47);font-size:inherit;\">We’ve made certain that from the second you click the button below…</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style